== 製作緣起 ==
該片改編自[[愛麗絲·華克|愛麗絲·華克]]的[[普利策奖|普立茲獎]]得獎小說《[[紫色姐妹花|紫色姐妹花]]》<ref>{{cite web |last1=Edemariam |first1=Aida |title=Interview: Alice Walker |url=https://www.theguardian.com/books/2007/jun/23/featuresreviews.guardianreview23 |website=''[[衛報|The Guardian]]'' |date=2007-06-23 |accessdate=2019-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191115182239/https://www.theguardian.com/books/2007/jun/23/featuresreviews.guardianreview23 |archive-date=2019-11-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。導演[[史蒂芬·史匹柏|史蒂芬·史匹柏]]在製片人[[凱斯琳·甘迺迪_(電影監製)|凱斯琳·甘迺迪]]的推薦下讀到了原著小說{{sfn|理查·席克爾|2017|p=108}}，剛讀到時雖然喜歡但沒有拍成電影的想法，數月後他重讀，發現「再也不能釋懷」{{sfn|Taylor|1997|p=171-172}}。史匹柏明白他將導演的這部片與他先前的作品風格迥異，題材也是全新的，令有意改革的他既期待又有點擔心{{sfn|Taylor|1997|p=24, 170-172}}。史匹柏對外宣稱這是他「第一次對自己的作品感到滿意」{{sfn|Taylor|1997|p=177}}。

== 上映與評價 ==
該片於1985年12月18日在美國上映<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl71992833/weekend/ |title=The Color Purple |publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |accessdate=2019-12-02 |archive-date=2021-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210701021940/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl71992833/weekend/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，獲得不少影評人的讚美<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/color_purple/|title=The Color Purple (1985)|publisher=Fandango Media|work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2019-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190512042621/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/color_purple/|archive-date=2019-05-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Ebert|first=Roger|title=The Color Purple|date=1985-12-20|work=''[[芝加哥太陽報|Chicago Sun Times]]''|url=http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/19851220/REVIEWS/512200302|accessdate=2010-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101031095633/http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F19851220%2FREVIEWS%2F512200302|archive-date=2010-10-31|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=The Color Purple|date=1984-12-31|work=''[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]''|url=https://variety.com/1984/film/reviews/the-color-purple-1200426436/|accessdate=2010-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151101010435/http://variety.com/1984/film/reviews/the-color-purple-1200426436/|archive-date=2015-11-01|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Maslin|first=Janet|title=Film: 'The Color Purple,' from Steven Spielberg|date=1985-12-18|work=''[[紐約時報|The New York Times]]''|url=https://www.nytimes.com/books/97/06/15/reviews/spielberg-color.html|accessdate=2010-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090410074208/http://www.nytimes.com/books/97/06/15/reviews/spielberg-color.html|archive-date=2009-04-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。原著作者華克也十分滿意，但片中涉及種族議題的內容引發了爭論和批評{{sfn|Taylor|1997|p=177-179}}{{sfn|理查·席克爾|2017|p=108}}<ref>{{cite news|last=Clegg II,|first=Legrand H.|title=Bad Black Roles In 'Purple'|date=1986-02-16|work=''[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]]''|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1986-02-16/entertainment/ca-8496_1_black-family-black-youths-black-man|accessdate=2010-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110314045850/http://articles.latimes.com/1986-02-16/entertainment/ca-8496_1_black-family-black-youths-black-man|archive-date=2011-03-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

